title: Tony Travers on the 2016 London Mayoral Election
itunes:author: Professor Tony Travers, Martin Rogers
description: Contributor(s): Professor Tony Travers, Martin Rogers | On 5 May 2016 the people of London will go to the polls to elect the city’s new Mayor. We sat down with Professor Tony Travers to discuss the potential candidates and the key issues which could decide how Londoners vote.
